Text tokens differ from surface tokens because they require higher contrast ratios to ensure accessible colour pairings. Some text tokens serve specific functions, such as text-heading or text-link, while others are more flexible. All text tokens must be used in accordance with the brand guidelines. **Avoid using restricted text tokens**, and always consult the guidelines if you’re unsure which tokens to apply.

{% tokens
   title="Brand text tokens"
   tokens=[{tokenName: "text-body", description: "Use for paragraph text and UI elements - labels, buttons, inputs etc", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-body", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-heading", description: "Use for headings only. Note: Using text-heading on anything other than headings may produce unexpected results in multi-brand applications.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-heading", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-link", description: "Use for text links only. Note: In Westpac this colour is exactly the same as text-primary however this may not be the case in other brands.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-link", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-muted", description: "Use for text that requires less emphasis like hint text etc.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-muted", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-primary", description: "Use with caution and in accordance with the brand guidelines. Tip: If your text is a link always use the text-link token.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-primary", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-hero", description: "Use for text that requires more emphasis, call outs, quotes etc.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-hero", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-holler", description: "Use for text that requires more emphasis, call outs, quotes etc. Note: GEL cannot endorse the use of this colour token until it's approved and documented as part of the Master Brand. This applies to all our brands.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-holler", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-mono", description: "Similar to surface-mono, text-mono is white in light mode and black in dark mode. It’s typically used for UI elements like buttons, tabs, panel heading etc.", fillColour: "surface-muted", textColour: "text-mono", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-reversed", description: "Similar to surface-reversed, text-reversed is always white. Use with caution, in dark mode white creates too much contrast which defeats the object of reducing glare. Tip: Try using text-mono", fillColour: "surface-muted", textColour: "text-reversed", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}] /%}

{% tokens
   title="Alert text tokens"
   tokens=[{tokenName: "text-success", description: "Only for success alert messages, do not use for anything else. Tip: Use the pre-built alert message components.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-success", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-info", description: "Only for info alert messages, do not use for anything else. Tip: Use the pre-built alert message components.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-info", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-warning", description: "Only for warning alert messages, do not use for anything else. Tip: Use the pre-built alert message components.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-warning", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-danger", description: "Only for danger alert messages, do not use for anything else. Tip: Use the pre-built alert message components.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-danger", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}, {tokenName: "text-system-error", description: "Only for system error alert messages, do not use for anything else. Tip: Use the pre-built alert message components.", strokeColour: "border-muted-soft", textColour: "text-system-error", circleType: "textColour", restricted: false, new: false}] /%}
